Media Mouse
This program turns a wireless mouse (or any mouse, however a wired mouse would be rather useless) into a remote control for your media player.

Installation:
python setup.py install

Command Line Usage:
mediamouse [media player]
Where [media player] is either banshee or amarok

Usage:
Right-Click - Next Song
Left-Click - Previous Song
Mousewheel-Up - Volume Up
Mousewheel-Down - Volume Down
Escape - Quit Program
